#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_walls/init.lua:250
msgid ""
"A piece of wall. It cannot be jumped over with a simple jump. When multiple "
"of these are placed to next to each other, they will automatically build a "
"nice wall structure."
msgstr ""
"Un pedazo de pared. No se puede saltar con un simple salto. Cuando varios de "
"estos se colocan uno al lado del otro, construirán automáticamente una "
"bonita estructura de pared."

